168
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,960
I believe the day we reunite with our junior sister

169
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,000
will come soon.

170
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,210
Alright, that's a wrap.

171
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,450
Come on, let's prepare for the next scene.

172
