176
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,040
Completely unaffected.

177
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:57,000
Well, you should consider

178
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,200
which manager is handling this artist.

179
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,000
Enough.

