00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,720
What's wrong with me?

183
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:07,580
I'm doing fine.

184
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,600
Looking at all this equipment,

185
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,330
