193
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,000
You shoot whatever I tell you to shoot, got it?

194
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:38,840
Come on,

195
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,400
the cinematographer said

196
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:41,760
